item.description: library(tidyverse) ## ── Attaching packages ─────────────────────────────────────── tidyverse 1.3.0 ── ## ✓ ggplot2 3.3.3 ✓ purrr 0.3.4 ## ✓ tibble 3.0.5 ✓ dplyr 1.0.3 ## ✓ tidyr 1.1.2 ✓ stringr 1.4.0 ## ✓ readr 1.4.0 ✓ forcats 0.5.0 ## ── Conflicts ────────────────────────────────────────── tidyverse_conflicts() ── ## x dplyr::filter() masks stats::filter() ## x dplyr::lag() masks stats::lag() library(ggplot2) library(waffle) volleyballstats <- read_csv("volleyballgamelogs2020.csv") ## ## ── Column specification ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── ## cols( ## .default = col_double(), ## Date = col_date(format = ""), ## Team = col_character(), ## Opponent = col_character(), ## HomeAway = col_character(), ## Result = col_character(), ## MS = col_logical() ## ) ## ℹ Use `spec()` for the full column specifications.
